 "edits": [
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1358",
   "jp_len": 97,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "{00}ゃ{00}3{00}だ{00}ェ{00}>{00}死{00}{01}{01}官{00}{01}{01}艦{00}{01}{01}艦{00}{01}{01}Sぁあいうえおかダチッツテ{01}デ、トドナ。ネハバパ·々ビベブミメちっつぞて·{00}！機{01}M開とな、{00}{01}！国{00}Mぬでな、{00}{01}ぁうわぁぁぁ唔！！",
   "zh_hex": "1500420010002b005300dd00a70001018f00010190000101900001011415161718191a1b6566676869016a026b6c6d036f70717204077377757a7c2c2d2e292f040006920113c02a3302000106a1001368293302000115184b151515e81def97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x13e8",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "小心！来了！",
   "zh_hex": "15e83ee82d06d9e7ba060000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x141c",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "碍事啊……你们",
   "zh_hex": "15e8c6efb8e7c30909e7b8e7bb0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1442",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这一来、入侵者也都收拾得差不多了……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9efb6efcf02e891ea46ef6ee7c0e840e926eae6e80ae9c7e7b5e7e9e7ba09090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1457",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "接下来就只剩你一个了……西格·韦德纳",
   "zh_hex": "15efceef4defcfe7c5ef32ea3ae7b8efb6e828e7ba0909e7f8e824ef4bebaee82ce8820000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1486",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……啧！！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e9faef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x14b4",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "艾因·雷维！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e8d6ef3304e8afea54060600000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x14ee",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "真讨厌、你干嘛气成那样啊、{00}西格·韦德纳？",
   "zh_hex": "15e820e9f7eb2b02e7b8e8d3e936e8ede837e7b7e7dae7c30200e7f8e82404ebaee82ce88205000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1514",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "要不是你们偷走了那台西斯库德、也不会{00}闹成这样啊",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2ae7b5e7b6e7b8e7bbebb4e890e7bae7b7ea16e7f8e7c8e9b3e82c02e7c0e7b5e7e200ead8e837e7b9e7dae7c3000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1562",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "为什么、艾因……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c1e7dde7bd02e8d6ef3309090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1577",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "为什么、要把我们卖给联邦！？就因为这{00}样、瑟拉她……！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c1e7dde7bd02ef2ae81befcce7bbec4ce839ef2eefaaef9705e7c5ef33e7c1e7b900e7da02e8aae7c2e88e0909ef97ef970000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x15bc",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哼、同伴被杀这种事、对你来说就无所谓{00}吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b302e85dea72e7f1e89be7b9e7d1efb802e7bee7b8efcfe7ede7c5e7dce7fbe92b00e8020500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x15e1",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你这人、可真够冷血的啊",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7b9efb202e7c4e820e920eb4ee9f6e7b4e7c3000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1614",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "回答我！艾因！！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef52ea96efccef97e8d6ef33ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1646",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "真麻烦……",
   "zh_hex": "15e820ea36e95b0909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x165c",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不过是毁掉一个人偶罢了、你就气得这样{00}血涌上头……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ef36e7b6e97ce9d3efb6e828efb2ea85eaefe7ba02e7b8e7c5e8ede80ae7b9e7da00e9f6ed82ef4ce92e090900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x16ad",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……你这混蛋！！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b8e7b9ea41ea6def97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x16e6",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哎呀哎呀……这样下去、可就连好好谈一{00}谈都做不到了啊",
   "zh_hex": "15e9dce9c6e9dce9c60909e7b9e7daef4de7eb02e7c4e7c5e86ee7c7e7c7eaf4efb600eaf4e840e81ce7b5e7d7e7bae7c3000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x170c",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "嘛、你要是这么想打、那也行……",
   "zh_hex": "15e93602e7b8ef2ae7b6e7b9e7bde7e6e7f502e7b7e7c0efd609090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1753",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那我就奉陪你到底吧！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7efcce7c5eac1ef42e7b8e7d7e9b4e7d0ef97ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1793",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啧……就这点能耐！",
   "zh_hex": "15e9fa0909e7c5e7b9e822e7c6ecfbef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x179f",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "瑟拉的仇、就由我来报了！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e8aae7c2e7b4eaa302e7c5e8a6efccefcfe913e7baef97ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x17d8",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可恶！竟在这种……地方……！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7deef97ef2cef29e7b9e7d10909ef63efb10909ef97ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1818",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "呀啊啊！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e9c6e7c3e7c30606000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1853",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……嗯？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e86505000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1881",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在、在这儿……总算找到友军了……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2902ef29e7b9eb7c0909e881e889e9d2e7d7e960e7e0e7ba0909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x18ad",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "别动队的幸存者吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e5ef30e7c9e7b4ea8de993ef6ee80205000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x18d3",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊、是！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c302e7b6060000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x18dc",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "您是突击队的西格·韦德纳中尉吧？我是{00}……",
   "zh_hex": "15e835e7b6e8b6e7cce7c9e7b4e7f8e824ef4bebaee82ce882ef4eefc6e7d005efcce7b600090900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x190d",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "有工夫自我介绍、就给我退下！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7cbeae4e830efb5efccea84ec8702e7c5e839efcce880ef4def970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1942",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……诶？",
   "zh_hex": "150909eaf3050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1964",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我是说、让你后退、快走开……不然你会{00}死的",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7b6e7ed02e7f9e7b8e7fee88002e85fe890e7fa0909e7b5e7efe7b8e7e200ef6ae7b400000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1998",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "等、等一下！你说退下……{00}那中尉你呢！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e82602e826878906e7b8e7ede88089090900e7b7c086e7b8e907060500000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x19cf",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我要打倒那家伙",
   "zh_hex": "15efccef2ae7f5e848e7b7e7dfe7fd0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x19f5",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那太乱来了！敌人有那么多……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e86ae976efcfe7baef97e7e3efb2e7cbe7b7e7bde7e90909ef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a26",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "数量不多",
   "zh_hex": "15e914e851e7b5e7e90000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a6a",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "等等！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e826e8260605000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a74",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……真是的！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e820e7b6e7b4ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1aa1",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……我应该说过、让你退下了吧？",
   "zh_hex": "150909efcce873e898e7edef3602e7f9e7b8e880ef4de7bae7d0050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ad0",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我怎么可能、丢下西格中尉一个人逃走啊{00}！",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7f2e7bde7c4e7c602ebb0ef4de7f8e824ef4eefc6efb6e828efb2e8c2e890e7c300ef97000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1af0",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我也要一起战斗！",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7c0ef2aefb6e847ef28e7ffef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b18",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……",
   "zh_hex": "150909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b21",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……随你",
   "zh_hex": "150909e9a1e7b8000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b50",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d0909ef97ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b84",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这下就结束了、艾因！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9ef4de7c5e868e895e7ba02e8d6ef33ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1bd2",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "『主人！！』",
   "zh_hex": "150ce954efb2ef97ef970d000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c00",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "您没事吧、主人？",
   "zh_hex": "15e835e7d8efb8e7d002e954efb20500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c28",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……",
   "zh_hex": "150909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c4c",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……主人？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e954efb205000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c6f",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "竟敢擅自行动……！是谁让你做这种事的{00}？",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2ce8cdeb5defb5efd6ef300909ef97e7b6e923e7f9e7b8e81ce7b9e7d1efb8e7b4000500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ca6",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "主人有危险",
   "zh_hex": "15e954efb2e7cbe935e9320000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ce5",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……",
   "zh_hex": "150909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d0f",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "什……！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dd0909ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d38",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "难道！",
   "zh_hex": "15e866e82a060000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d65",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "瑟拉！！你、你是瑟拉吗！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e8aae7c2ef97ef97e7b802e7b8e7b6e8aae7c2e802ef9705000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d98",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……",
   "zh_hex": "150909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1da1",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……不、我是瑟蕾因·伊克斯贝利……",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b5028be7b6e8aae84cef3304e969e7d5e7c8e857e82e09090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1dd7",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我是侍奉艾因主人之人",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7b6eca8eac1e8d6ef33e954efb2e7cdefb2000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1dfc",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "住手啊、瑟拉！！你认不出我了吗！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e859ef66e7c302e8aae7c2ef97ef97e7b8e8a0e7b5efbeefcce7bae802ef9705000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e47",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "对主人加以危害者……予以排除",
   "zh_hex": "15e7bee954efb2e854e7f3e935e988ef6e0909efb7e7f3ea67e974000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e8b",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "住手！瑟蕾因！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e859ef66ef97e8aae84cef33ef97ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ec3",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔！主人！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e81def97e954efb2ef970500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1efc",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "主人……",
   "zh_hex": "15e954efb20909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f1e",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我应该说过了吧……不许你擅自行动",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce873e898e7edef36e7bae7d00909e7b5e8a7e7b8eb5defb5efd6ef3000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f53",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可是、再那样下去、我判断主人会有危险{00}……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7b602e80be7b7e7daef4de7eb02efcceb29e982e954efb2e7e2e7cbe935e9320009090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f8a",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "判断……？谁让你去做判断了！？",
   "zh_hex": "15eb29e982090905e923e7f9e7b8e7ebe81ceb29e982e7baef970500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1fa4",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你只要退下、专心做好支援就行了！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8ef32ef2ae880ef4d02eb4be82de81ce7c7e883e863e7c5efd6e7baef97000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1fd8",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……遵命",
   "zh_hex": "150909ec40e8530000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2006",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "呵呵……怎么样、西格？和昔日的恋人重{00}逢、是什么感觉？",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3def3d0909e7f2e7bde7da02e7f8e82405e7d3ec55e98ae7b4ee20b4e8a100ed1102e7b6e7dde7bde87de8ae050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x203e",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "艾因……！你这家伙、{00}对瑟拉做了什么！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e8d6ef33090906e7b8e7b9e7dfe7fd0200e7bee8aae7c2e81ce7bae7dde7bd06050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x206e",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哎呀……你不高兴吗、西格？昔日的恋人{00}明明还活着",
   "zh_hex": "15e9dce9c60909e7b8e7b5e812eabae80202e7f8e82405ec55e98ae7b4ee20b400ef39ef39e7f7e8d4e86d0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x20ad",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我在问你、到底对她做了什么！！",
   "zh_hex": "15efccef29e997e7b802e7d7e9b4e7bee88ee81ce7bae7dde7bdef97ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x20db",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我只不过是、让那东西变成了与它相称的{00}模样罢了",
   "zh_hex": "15efccef32e7b5ef36e7b602e7f9e7b7e8bae7f8e955e837e7bae832e978e8b1ea01e7b400ea91e7daeaefe7ba000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x20fa",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "刚才说过了吧？那只是人偶",
   "zh_hex": "15e8bce836e7edef36e7bae7d005e7b7ef32e7b6efb2ea85000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2130",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……啥！？",
   "zh_hex": "150909eabe06050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2154",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……人偶！？",
   "zh_hex": "150909efb2ea85ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2178",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那东西不需要心、也不需要意志、只要有{00}机能就够了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e8bae7f8e7b5e92def2ae82d02e7c0e7b5e92def2aef3cea1802ef32ef2ae7cb00e7e4e7c6e7c5e920e7ba000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2199",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……没错！就像这样！！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7d8e885ef97e7c5e8e9e7b9e7daef97ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x21cf",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……唔！？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e81def9705000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x21f2",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "小心、西格中尉！",
   "zh_hex": "15e83ee82d02e7f8e824ef4eefc6ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x222c",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "正是用上了瑟蕾因·伊克斯贝利这件{00}工具、才头一次成为可能……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3be7b6d8b2e7bae8aae84cef3304e969e7d5e7c8e857e82ee7b9e99100eae4ea1402e836e92e87e864e837e7c1e7c4e7c609090000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2248",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这就是迪斯帕达的另一种力量！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7c5e7b6ea11e7c8eb01ef2be7b4e99b87e7d1dae8510600000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x227f",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔、迎击！",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d02e931e7ccef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x22bb",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……太慢了！！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e86ae979e7baef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x22f5",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "什么！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dde7bdef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x232c",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "呵呵……和刚才相比、立场可就反过来了{00}呢",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3def3d0909e7d3e8bce836e8b1e82502e86be876e7c4e7c5e87cef36d9e7ba00e90700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x235d",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……怎么回事？那家伙的反应速度、突然{00}就……",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7f2e7bdef52efb805e7b7e7dfe7fde7b4e87ce873e9dae96d02e8b6e7ef00e7c509090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2390",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "虽说是姐妹机、西斯库德说到底不过是旧{00}人类也能用的通用型……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b8e7ede7b6e921ebbde7e402e7f8e7c8e9b3e82ce7ede7d7e9b4e7b5ef36e7b6eac800b4e841e7c0e7c6d8e7b4c2d8e9770909000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x23b1",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "和专为新人类开发的迪斯帕达、机能上有{00}着天差地别",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d3eb4be7c1ef8aefb2e841e7fae870e7b4ea11e7c8eb01ef2b02e7e4e7c6ef4ce7cb00e86de844e9c7ef63e7e50000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x23d0",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "好了……这下就要永别了、西格",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c7e7ba0909e7b9ef4de7c5ef2ae9bfe7e5e7ba02e7f8e8240000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x23e2",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "就怀着对那个女人的幻想、去死吧！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c5eb03e86de7bee7b7e828efadefb2e7b4ed53e7e602e7ebef6ae7d0ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2427",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……西格中尉！！我来掩护、你快退下！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7f8e824ef4eefc6ef97ef97efccefcfec72e8e002e7b8e85fe880ef4def970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x245b",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不……还没完！我要亲手干掉那家伙！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b50909e7f7e7d8e87eef97efccef2ae894ef66e8d3e9d3e7b7e7dfe7fdef97ef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2490",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "带着那样的伤、太勉强了！冷静点、西格{00}中尉！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e937e86de7b7e7dae7b4e8f902e86aeb2ae8ade7baef97eb4eeab3e82202e7f8e82400ef4eefc6ef97ef970000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x24c5",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你又懂什么！！那家伙把瑟拉……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e8f1e8b0e7dde7bdef97ef97e7b7e7dfe7fde81be8aae7c20909ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2515",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……我懂的！",
   "zh_hex": "1509098be8b0e7b406000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2521",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "瑟拉的事、连我也是知道的呀！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e8aae7c2e7b4a902e86e8be7c0e7b6e85ae82ae7b4e9c6060600000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x253b",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "还有你曾经喜欢过她、这事我也知道！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f7e7cbe7b8ea2ae8b7ecc0ea92ef36e88e02e7b9a98be7c0e85ae82a06060000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x256f",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……唔！？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e81def9705000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2592",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你都忘了吗、西格！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e840ea4de7bae80202e7f8e824ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x265d",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你是……！难道、你是蜜安吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7b6090906e866e82a02e7b8e7b6e98ee7fce8020500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2694",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……你还记得我啊、西格",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b8e7f7e996e80aefcce7c302e7f8e824000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x26cb",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "没想到、连布拉德队长的女儿都现身了{00}……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d8e7e6e7d702e86ee831e7c2e82ce7c9ef34e7b4b0eb7ce840e82fe88de7ba000909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x26e5",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这真成同学会了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e820e837e85deb55e7e2e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2711",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "艾因·雷维……我绝不会让你打倒西格",
   "zh_hex": "15e8d6ef3304e8afea5409098be91ce7b5e7e2e7f9e7b8e7f5e848e7f8e82400000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2744",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "蜜安！我……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e98ee7fcef97efcc0909ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x276b",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……求你了、西格、就这一次、听我的话{00}好吗",
   "zh_hex": "150909e93ae7b8e7ba02e7f8e82402e7c5e7b9efb6e86402e8d1efcce7b4e81f00e7c7e802000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2789",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "要是在这里倒下、就什么{00}都没了、不是吗？所以……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2ae7b6ef29e7b9ef31e8488902e7c5e7dde7bd00e840e7d8e7ba02e7b5e7b6e80205e7fbe7f3090900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x27c4",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……",
   "zh_hex": "150909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x27cd",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……好、蜜安",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7c702e98ee7fc0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x27d9",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这次就乖乖撤退……这样行了吧？把撤退{00}点告诉我",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e864e7c5e9a3e9a3e90ae8800909e7b9e7daefd6e7bae7d005e81be90ae88000e822e8e5ead6efcc000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x281f",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这边……！只要能逃到这里……总算有办{00}法了！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e8990909ef97ef32ef2ae7c6e8c2e7d7e7b9ef310909e881e889e7cbe8ea00e84ee7baef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x283a",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "刚才收到通信说、友军的战舰已经赶到附{00}近了……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8bce836e926e7d7ef59e90fe7ed02e960e7e0e7b4ef28e7d4ef3ae8b7ea04e7d7eaf800efd8e7ba0909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2874",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……明白",
   "zh_hex": "150909ef39e8090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x28a1",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "接下来就剩你了！艾因·雷维！！",
   "zh_hex": "15b789d9e7c5ea3ae7b8e7ba06e8d6ef3304e8afea540606000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x28d2",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那走吧！西格！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e890e7d0ef97e7f8e824ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x28fe",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我是阿伽玛号的汉肯中佐！你们那边没事{00}吧！？",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7b6e7d2e8e8e845e833e7b4ef82e93def4eefbaef97e7b8e7bbe7b7e899e7d8efb800e7d0ef970500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x293a",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我是西格·韦德纳中尉、现在、正遭受敌{00}人的追击",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7b6e7f8e824ef4bebaee82ce882ef4eefc602e82fef2902ef3beb1ee8c8e7e300efb2e7b4e8dde7cc00000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x296f",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你说是西格·韦德纳！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7ede7b6e7f8e824ef4bebaee82ce882ef9705000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2996",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……夏亚大佐！？",
   "zh_hex": "150909ef37e7d6efa5efbaef9705000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x29c6",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "竟有人来碍事……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2ce7cbefb2efcfe8c6efb809090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x29d7",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "嘛、这次就先到这里吧……撤了、瑟蕾因",
   "zh_hex": "15e93602e7b9e864e7c5ef8be7d7e7b9ef31e7d00909e90ae7ba02e8aae84cef33000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2a0a",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "遵命……主人",
   "zh_hex": "15ec40e8530909e954efb20000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2a38",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……艾因！？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e8d6ef33ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2a66",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这次、就算是打个照面吧？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e86402e7c5e889e7b6e7f5e828ea1ae862e7d005000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2a7c",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你们的对手、就交给他们来当吧",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7bbe7b4e7beef6602e7c5e861e839e80ce7bbefcfef53e7d000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2abb",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "要是能活下来、就再会吧、西格……{00}那么、回头见",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2ae7b6e7c6e8d489d902e7c5e80be7e2e7d002e7f8e824090900e7b7e7bd028ce92ee85c000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2afa",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……",
   "zh_hex": "150909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2b28",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "艾因",
   "zh_hex": "15e8d6ef330000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2b54",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "西格·韦德纳……没想到你竟然在奥古",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f8e824ef4bebaee82ce8820909e7d8e7e6e7d7e7b8ef2ce7efef29e82be84d00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2b6b",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "还有、那台MS……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f7e7cb02e7b7ea16efa7ef9e09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2b77",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你说的艾因、就是那个艾因·雷维吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7ede7b4e8d6ef3302e7c5e7b6e7b7e828e8d6ef3304e8afea54e802050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2ba9",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……是啊、那家伙是瑟拉的……仇人",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b6e7c302e7b7e7dfe7fde7b6e8aae7c2e7b40909eaa3efb200000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2bd7",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……什么！？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7dde7bdef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2c05",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "克瓦特罗大尉！旧话以后再说！敌人逼近{00}了！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d5e99fe7cfe7ecefa5efc6ef97eac8e81fe7f3e7fee80be7edef97e7e3efb2ebf6efd800e7baef97000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2c39",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……也对",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d0909e7c0e7be000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2c4f",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "西格中尉、你还能继续战斗吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f8e824ef4eefc602e7b8e7f7e7c6e9d6e9adef28e7ffe80205000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2c79",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊、我没事",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c302efcce7d8efb80000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2ca0",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么、迎击敌人！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02e931e7cce7e3efb2ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2cad",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "汉肯舰长！让MS队出击！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef82e93de7d4ef34ef97e7f9efa7ef9ee7c9efbee7ccef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2cd9",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哦、收到！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e91902e926e7d7ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2cee",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "全机、立刻出击！迎击提坦斯的MS！",
   "zh_hex": "15efb4e7e402e86be91fefbee7ccef97e931e7cce821e843e7c8e7b4efa7ef9eef97000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2d2c",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "敌方部队、毫无反应！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e3efb1ef70e7c902ea0ae7dce87ce873ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2d55",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "好！趁敌方援军还没赶到、撤退吧！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c7ef97e9eae7e3efb1e863e7e0e7f7e7d8ea04e7d702e90ae880e7d0ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2d6a",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "全部队、撤退！",
   "zh_hex": "15efb4ef70e7c902e90ae880ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2d9a",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是奥古本部下达的命令",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6e82be84defa6ef70ef4def2be7b4e853e94e00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2da7",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "命西格·韦德纳中尉与阿伽玛会合、此后{00}一同行动",
   "zh_hex": "15e853e7f8e824ef4bebaee82ce882ef4eefc6e832e7d2e8e8e845e7e2efc002e7cae7fe00efb6e85defd6ef300000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2de3",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "对了、西格中尉夺来的那台新型机呢？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7bee7ba02e7f8e824c086ea17d9e7b4e7b7ea16ef8ae977e7e4e9070500000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2e16",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "听说运用就交给我们负责",
   "zh_hex": "15e8d1e7ede986efb3e7c5e861e839efcce7bbe92ceba60000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2e25",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "正好也有高达Mk-Ⅱ在、用来评估性能{00}再合适不过了",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3be7c7e7c0e7cbe812ef2befa7eedeef71eee1ef2902efb3efcfee9eed1fe951e7c600e80befc0ef41e7b5ef36e7ba000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2e4f",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "西格中尉、你也没意见吧？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f8e824ef4eefc602e7b8e7c0e7d8ef3ce85ce7d005000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2e79",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "…没异议",
   "zh_hex": "1509e7d8eb32e8e30000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2e83",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "若能与那台新型机一同行动、对我反倒方{00}便",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e7e7c6e832e7b7ea16ef8ae977e7e487e85d9fef3002e7be8be87ce848d000e8fa000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2eb7",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "西格中尉？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f8e824ef4eefc6050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2eda",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那台叫西斯库德的MS、艾因也牵涉其中",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7ea16e8c1e7f8e7c8e9b3e82ce7b4efa7ef9e02e8d6ef33e7c0eb94ece6e8cfef4e000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2ef3",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "他一定、会现身来夺回那台MS的",
   "zh_hex": "15e80cefb6e86702e7e2e82fe88defcfea17ef52e7b7ea16efa7ef9ee7b400000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2f27",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……西格中尉",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7f8e824ef4eefc6000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2f30",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你们过去之间有过什么、我虽不清楚……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7bbef36e7ebe7cde8fce7cbef36e7dde7bd02efcce8b8e7b5e995ebd309090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2f64",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……不知道、就请你别多嘴",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b5e85ae82a02e7c5e83ae7b8e7e5e7e9eae20000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2f76",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这是我和他之间的事",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7b6efcce7d3e80ce7cde8fce7b4efb80000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2fa1",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……",
   "zh_hex": "150909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2faa",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……和刚才白色MS的驾驶员有关吗？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7d3e8bce836e809e89f1314e7b4e953e975e849e7cbe8bbe8020500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2fe7",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……没心情提旧事",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7d8e82de88be821eac8a900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2ff9",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "就这事吗？那我回房间了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c5e7b9efb8e80205e7b7efccef52ecd8e8fce7ba000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3073",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……",
   "zh_hex": "150909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x307c",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "真是的……他这个人、可真不好相处啊",
   "zh_hex": "15e820e7b6e7b40909e80ce7b9e828efb202e7c4e820e7b5e7c7e8b1e903e7c3000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x30af",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "往事…",
   "zh_hex": "15e911efb8090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x30d2",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……嗯？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e865050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x30f5",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……瑟蕾因·伊克斯贝利、是曾经做过他{00}搭档的女子",
   "zh_hex": "150909e8aae84cef3304e969e7d5e7c8e857e82e02e7b6ea2ae8b7e81cef36e80c00eb09ed78e7b4b0e886000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3125",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那、怎么？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b702e7f2e7bd050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x314b",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那台白色MS的驾驶员、当时也被称作{00}瑟蕾因……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7ea16e809e89f1314e7b4e953e975e84902c4ef2de7c0e7f1ea01ef2f00e8aae84cef330909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3166",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "他口中的『往事』、是不是也把这件事算{00}了进去呢？",
   "zh_hex": "15e80ceabdef4ee7b40ce911efb80d02e7b6e7b5e7b6e7c0e81be7b9e991efb8e88900e7bae892e7ebe907050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3183",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么、他……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02e80c0909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x31ab",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……克瓦特罗大尉？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7d5e99fe7cfe7ecefa5efc6050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x321e",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊、西格……中尉",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c302e7f8e8240909ef4eefc60000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3244",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……蜜安",
   "zh_hex": "150909e98ee7fc000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3269",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那个、嗯、这个……好久不见……是吧？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e82802e86502e7b9e8280909e7c7e9dbe7b5e85c0909e7b6e7d005000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x329a",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "离刚才那场战斗、应该没过多久吧？",
   "zh_hex": "15e901e8bce836e7b7e876ef28e7ff02e873e898e7d8ef36e7e9e9dbe7d005000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x32d0",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不是啦！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5e7b6ec0fef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x32db",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我是说、自打仗结束之后、已经过了好一{00}阵子了嘛！！",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7b6e7ed02efb5e7f5ea37e868e895e7cde7fe02ef3ae8b7ef36e7bae7c7efb600eb48e886e7bae936ef97ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x330e",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……或许是吧",
   "zh_hex": "150909e905e8a7e7b6e7d0000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3337",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我说、西格……",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7ed02e7f8e82409090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3342",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你和艾因他们之间发生过什么、我虽然不{00}知道……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7d3e8d6ef33e80ce7bbe7cde8fce870b6ef36e7dde7bd028be8b8e7efe7b500e85ae82a09090000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x337c",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……不知道反倒好",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b5e85ae82ae87ce848e7c70000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x33a8",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可、可是！西格、你一脸那么痛苦的表情{00}……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c402e7c4e7b6ef97e7f8e82402e7b8efb6eb69e7b7e7bdea0be9e6e7b4e9e7e88b00090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x33dd",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那样的话、能不能、让我一个人静一{00}静？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e7dae7b4e81f02e7c6e7b5e7c602e7f9efccefb6e828efb2eab3efb600eab3050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x33f1",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "看到旧相识的脸、实在令我难受",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f6e7d7eac8e8b1e92fe7b4eb6902e87fef29e94eefcce866e8c80000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3421",
   "jp_len": 6,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c309090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3427",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "对、对不起",
   "zh_hex": "15e7be02e7bee7b5e847000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x347e",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……",
   "zh_hex": "150909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x34af",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可恶！我这是在干什么……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7deef97efcce7b9e7b6ef29e8d3e7dde7bd0909ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x82f2",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "呜哇！不、不好……！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e8d9ea88ef97e7b502e7b5e7c70909ef97ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8382",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "一路辛苦了",
   "zh_hex": "15efb6e8d2ea58e9e6e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x838f",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "感谢你、将这条『宇宙世纪路线』一直玩{00}到了最后",
   "zh_hex": "15e87de8b2e7b802e84ae7b9e9d40ce8bee8bfe83ceb99e8d2e9160defb6e875e97000e7d7e7bae8c5e7fe0000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x83af",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "另外、隆德·贝尔队的战斗、就先在此告{00}一段落了……",
   "zh_hex": "15e99be8f702ed16e82cef4be857e7e1e7c9e7b4ef28e7ff02e7c5ef8bef29e7cae8e500efb6ea6be92ae7ba0909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x83ce",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "游戏本身仍然可以继续、今后也请继续尽{00}情享受",
   "zh_hex": "15ea94ea3eefa6e88deab9e7efe7c4e7f3e9d6e9ad02efb9e7fee7c0e83ae9d6e9ade8f200e88bec06e8c80000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x83f3",
   "jp_len": 39,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "另外、为将本路线一直玩到最后的你、还{00}准备了特别关卡",
   "zh_hex": "15e99be8f702e7c1e84aefa6e8d2e916efb6e875e970e7d7e8c5e7fee7b4e7b802e7f700e87ae877e7bae7cfe7e5e8bbe80100000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x841a",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那是与我们分头、一直另行作战的大天使{00}队的特别演习",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7b6e832efcce7bbefaee92e02efb6e875e99befd6ef2fef28e7b4efa5e844e83f00e7c9e7b4e7cfe7e5ea2feab6000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x843b",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "与他们一战、检验一下你一路培养起来的{00}部队实力、也未尝不可",
   "zh_hex": "15e832e80ce7bbefb6ef2802ee40ea99efb6ef4de7b8efb6e8d2edfeec0be847efcfe7b400ef70e7c9e87fefb002e7c0e8b4eccfe7b5e7c40000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8460",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在自由对战中选择『特殊演习』、便可与{00}他们一战",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29efb5e8a6e7beef28ef4ee966eaaa0ce7cfed7bea2feab60d02e8fae7c4e83200e80ce7bbefb6ef280000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8485",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那么、『SD高达G世代DS』",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e7bd020cef9eef96e812ef2beed1e83ce8e7ef96ef9e0d0000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x84a9",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "今后也希望你、慢慢地尽情玩到最后",
   "zh_hex": "15efb9e7fee7c0e87be965e7b802e979e979ef63e8f2e88be970e7d7e8c5e7fe0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8522",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "谢谢你、一直陪着我这样一个靠不住的{00}舰长走到现在",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b2e8b2e7b80287e875ef42e86d8be7b9e7da87e828e8c7e7b5e859e7b400e7d4ef34e890e7d7e82fef290000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8541",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这条『平成高达路线』、就到此告一段落{00}了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e9d40ce887e837e812ef2be8d2e9160d02e7c5e7d7e7cae8e5efb6ea6be92a00e7ba000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x855f",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "虽说、我们预防者的战斗、已经到此结束{00}了……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b8e7ed02efcce7bbea5ae968ef6ee7b4ef28e7ff02ef3ae8b7e7d7e7cae868e89500e7ba090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8579",
   "jp_len": 38,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不过游戏本身还可以继续玩哦、今后也请{00}你继续尽情享受",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ef36ea94ea3eefa6e88de7f7e7c4e7f3e9d6e9ade970e91902efb9e7fee7c0e83a00e7b8e9d6e9ade8f2e88bec06e8c80000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x859f",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "为将这条路线一直玩到最后的你、还准备{00}了新的关卡哦",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c1e84ae7b9e9d4e8d2e916efb6e875e970e7d7e8c5e7fee7b4e7b802e7f7e87ae87700e7baef8ae7b4e8bbe801e9190000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x85c3",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那是与我们分头、一直在和提坦斯、新吉{00}翁作战的……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7b6e8328be7bbcde92e0287e875ef29e7d3e821e843e7c802ef8ae7d900ee88ef2fef28e7b40909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x85de",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……与隆德·贝尔队的特别演习哦",
   "zh_hex": "150909e832ed16e82cef4be857e7e1e7c9e7b4e7cfe7e5ea2feab6e9190000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x85f1",
   "jp_len": 38,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在自由对战中选择『特别演习』、就能和{00}他们交战哦",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29efb5e8a6e7beef28ef4ee966eaaa0ce7cfe7e5ea2feab60d02e7c5e7c6e7d300e80ce7bbe861ef28e91900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8617",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "请务必挑战",
   "zh_hex": "15e83ae94fe860eae7ef28000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8625",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那么、『SD高达G世代DS』",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e7bd020cef9eef96e812ef2beed1e83ce8e7ef96ef9e0d0000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8649",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "『自由对战的战火！冲锋吧、大天使号！{00}！』",
   "zh_hex": "150cefb5e8a6e7beef28e7b4ef28e8daef97e95ee967e7d002efa5e844e83fe833ef9700ef970d000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x86ca",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我是主天使号的舰长、娜塔尔·巴基露露{00}中佐",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7b6e954e844e83fe833e7b4e7d4ef3402e7eae945e7e1ef4be85be829e858e85800ef4eefba000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x86da",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "首先、请允许我向你一路以来出色的{00}指挥、致以敬意",
   "zh_hex": "15ef40b802e83aecade8a78b9de7b887e8d2e7f3d9afe89fe7b400e8c0e94902ea32e7f3ee38ef3c000000000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x86fc",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "多亏了你的协力、我们才得以一直奋战到{00}最后",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e9eab7e7bae7b8e7b4e8f6efb002efcce7bbe836e80ae7f3efb6e875ef46ef28e7d700e8c5e7fe0000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x871e",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这条『对手路线』、就到此结束了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e9d40ce7beef66e8d2e9160d02e7c5e7d7e7cae868e895e7ba00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8734",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "虽说、我们主天使队的战斗、已经到此结{00}束……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b8e7ed02efcce7bbe954e844e83fe7c9e7b4ef28e7ff02ef3ae8b7e7d7e7cae86800e8950909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x874d",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "游戏本身仍然可以继续、今后也请继续尽{00}情享受",
   "zh_hex": "15ea94ea3eefa6e88deab9e7efe7c4e7f3e9d6e9ad02efb9e7fee7c0e83ae9d6e9ade8f200e88bec06e8c8000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8771",
   "jp_len": 43,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "自由对战今后仍可继续、另外、只要选择{00}『特别演习』……",
   "zh_hex": "15efb5e8a6e7beef28efb9e7feeab9e7c4e9d6e9ad02e99be8f702ef32ef2ae966eaaa000ce7cfe7e5ea2feab60d09090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x879c",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "还能与隆德·贝尔、预防者进行联合演习",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f7e7c6e832ed16e82cef4be857e7e102ea5ae968ef6ee892efd6ef2eefc0ea2feab60000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x87ba",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我相信、以你的实力、与他们一战也定能{00}取胜",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce8b1e90f02e7f3e7b8e7b4e87fefb002e832e80ce7bbefb6ef28e7c0e867e7c600e987e8db000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x87df",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那么、『SD高达G世代DS』",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e7bd020cef9eef96e812ef2beed1e83ce8e7ef96ef9e0d0000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8803",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "今后也祝你武运长久",
   "zh_hex": "15efb9e7fee7c0ed97e7b8e8ece986ef34e9db00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x882a",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "西格·韦德纳……吗",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f8e824ef4bebaee82ce8820909e8020000"
  }
 ]
}
